#: e8b51d5d95164ae48656105aa7a84ad2
msgid "create app"
msgstr "создать приложение"

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:304 265092e5523a49ac994cfbc4a721c595
msgid ""
"We conduct a `PoC project with Geocloud.work "
"<https://www.geocloud.work/software/geoalert>`_ who enable to work "
"remotely with the licensed geospatial software."
