msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:310 c2e2b2e262864993a4ebeb9ff078e6ac
msgid ""
"It runs the virtual machine with minimum requirements for QGIS with a "
"preinstalled Mapflow plugin. Note that you have to run consequently the "
"Storage and the Desktop to get connected to the virtual machine with a "
"remote desktop."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:313 c385c9c6a51345a993462897e7ad066f
msgid "Run QGIS by clicking on the \"QGIS-Mapflow\" icon at the desktop workspace"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:323 1cc896972a964d1f8af56a06bd68538d
msgid "Run the plugin by clicking on the icon in the toolbar"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:334 1f98fcd1ecc44f679814476b6b596598
msgid ""
"❗️ To enable Mapflow oAuth login use the master password for QGIS which "
"is set to 123456"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:337 f41c3c495af6462e84028ea11f17157a
msgid ""
"After you click  the \"Login\" button you will be redirected to the "
"Mapflow login page in the browser. Use your existing `Mapflow.ai "
"<https://app.mapflow.ai>`_ login and password or create a new account to "
"start working with the plugin. You can also use Basic auth (disable \"Use"
" OAuth\" checkbox) with your Mapflow `Token "
"<https://app.mapflow.ai/account/api>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:340 d064ffc776754899a41d830c7a91d2c3
msgid ""
"You are all set up to use :doc:`Mapflow – QGIS </userguides/qgis_plugin>`"
" in Geocloud."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:343 99f6bb90c1704504ac8963191ce95fbb
msgid ""
"Note that you pay only for the up time in Geocloud. You spend your "
"regular credits for Mapflow (you get 250 credits for free upon the "
"registration). There are two prices for Storage / Computer in Geocloud - "
"*Stopped* and *Working*. The Stopped price is applied when Storage / "
"Computer is stopped. The Working price is applied when it is in the "
"working mode. 👉👉 You can stop your computer while doing some long-lasting"
" calculations in Mapflow to spend less."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/howto.rst:348 f6ef02cd66794439a359e4842aee777d
msgid "How to check images metadata in the 🌏 Global mosaic"
msgstr "Как проверить метаданные снимков в 🌏 Глобальной мозаике"

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:1 b29a48ef692a4245b7c2325256e9e4f4
msgid ""
"Mapflow Imagery Search enables searching metadata for mosaic providers "
"(e.g., ArcGIS World Imagery, Global mosaic)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:4 37ac83e7212c4177a38754c365e05232
msgid ""
"**🌏 Global mosaic** is the annually updated satellite imagery composite "
"covering most of the World. The mosaic is composed of \"Jilin\" Chinese "
"satellites imagery (RGB, 0.75–0.5 m/px). The preview is limited to zoom "
"14. **🌏 ArcGIS World Imagery** is a provider of the global coverage "
"composed of high and medium resolution satellite imagery and aerial "
"imagery, hosted by ESRI. The frequency of updating images is 1-5 years "
"depending on the territory."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:7 e70907d3d9954a11b7432eb49d653b59
msgid ""
"How to use :doc:`Mapflow – QGIS <qgis_plugin>` to search for mosaic's "
"metadata and run the analysis:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:9 9180aded07664e4eb7b1fd78b95b38f2
msgid "Switch to the Tab \"Imagery Search\""
msgstr "Перейдите на вкладку \"Imagery Search\"."

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:10
#: ede6031a358a4283b21c9b538cb61f64
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Set search filter parameters including the area (it can be your area of "
"analysis or a map canvas), period of time, cloud %, and the % of the "
"intersection with AOI."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:11
#: 05f5491fcd7c429a87a007202a6d9b13
msgid ""
"Select the \"Product type = Mosaic\" in the Search results. You will see "
"the mosaic image \"cutline\" indicating the specific image that is used "
"in the mosaic."
msgstr ""

#: f4cfd50c4dbf49a19e6562e6ab3d6e02
msgid "Search for Mosaic images"
msgstr "Поиск мозаичных снимков"

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:22
#: 3b2481aa3ddb49c5b6986518a3e7b1c3
msgid ""
"There are two types of products in the Imagery Search API available: * "
"The **Scene** product is available for ordering by request. Now you need "
"to contact us to order the specific image. * The **Mosaic** product is "
"available for instant analysis if the corresponding data provider is "
"linked to your Mapflow account."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:26
#: c70e901cb0184ae3938eb50dbf29033a
msgid ""
"Run the processing. The resulting area of analysis will be clipped by the"
" intersection with the area of analysis."
msgstr ""

#: 7e1d7b563893412795b5fbf433259980
msgid "Get results based on Mosaic analysis"
msgstr "Получение результатов на основе анализа мозаики"

#: ../../source/userguides/search_mosaic.rst:35
#: bd24d6f3ee8e44feba987cfd66ac7f94
msgid ""
"To run the processing over the whole area of analysis – just clear the "
"selection and use the **Data Source: 🌏 Global mosaic 2022** or the **Data"
" Source: 🌏 ArcGIS World Imagery**."
msgstr ""

